    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Automatically set and unset the term when the time is up.</p>\n<p>Check the &#8220;use schedule&#8221; checkbox in the category or tag management screen. You can set a time for each post to be added or removed from the category or tag.</p>\n<h4>Usage</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to category,tag or custom taxonomy management screen.</li>\n<li>Check the &#8220;Use scheduling&#8221; checkbox.</li>\n<li>Goto edit post screen then set datetime in &#8220;Schedule Terms&#8221; panel.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Credits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JJJ/wp-term-meta-ui/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WP Term Meta UI</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.3.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested WordPress 6.5.</li>\n<li>Update packages.</li>\n<li>Add reset button.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Load translation.</li>\n<li>Fix DateTimePicker format.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>fix ui.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Bug fix.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>fix ci.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First release.</li>\n</ul>\n"
